{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"一、观察细节：<div>她的声音很疲惫、很不舒服吗？语气怎么样？</div><div>二、侧面了解：</div><div>最近有没有去医院？是不是大姨妈来了？</div><div>三、直接提问：</div><div>我要不要现在过去陪你？</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7913,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492469100000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"DearJoey","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzXrk7kxiaxiarcZtoK5ibGvfiaxSOc4AUm4uYjslRRZQg8yWScKHibVDOuOqxTZic5HfXm3wFhibAvyqMy/0","content":"”你哪里不舒服？是感冒了还是亲戚来了？“（如果真的是身体不舒服，接下来就要问平常常用的药物，然后买好带过去。如果并不是真的身体不舒服，那就可能是女朋友想让小明陪，可以跟她说：“你呀在家里呆太久了，我带你出来散散心吧。”这时候可以选择陪女朋友出去玩，跟她多说说话，或者让她看一场自己踢的球，然后跟她聊聊天。后面这个是又踢到球又陪了女朋友。）","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7840,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492406626000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.注意观察细节——“没什么大事”那就是有事，“身体不太舒服”就是我希望得到安慰/照顾/陪伴；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.侧面了解——从朋友、女朋友家人处收集信息，判断是哪种可能性更大；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.直接提问——“哪里不舒服啦？肚子痛吗？”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.行动——选择的重点在于清晰什么事情更重要，如果觉得女朋友更重要，那么这时候的选择就是“我这边少了我也没关系，10分钟后到你家”。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7685,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492133835000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p>女朋友最后那句“没什么大事，就是身体不太舒服”，听着就是话里有话的意思。如果我是小明的话，我得多问几句了：</p><p>我可能会立马问她“身体哪里不舒啊？”有可能问完之后会<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">出现两种情况：</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">1是如果她较为详细和准确地说出具体不舒服的地方和症状，那么这个时候就可以接着跟她说“身体不舒服可是大事情，要赶紧上医院，要不我专门赶过去送你到医院看病？我挺担心你的啊！”通常这个时候如果是真得很不舒服，应该就会顺着话要求我过去带她看病了，踢球的事情就等下一次吧；但如果是轻微的问题，她也会自己说在家好好休息，毕竟我是真心紧张她且告诉她我担心她的，这种时候她心里应该是能够理解的，后面我还得多跟她说几句在家如何好好休息之类的话，这种情况最后踢球还是有着落的，但是等她身体好了之后最好不要细谈踢球的事情。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;2是如果她的回答是“</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">也没有特别的地方，就是感觉不舒服\"，那么这种情况多半就是故意无病呻吟，或者说是撒娇，这种情况会比较麻烦。我就得问一下她”嘿嘿，是不是因为思念我，所以患上相思病啦？“她多半会回答”才没有之类的“。按理说，这样应该就能够尽快撂电话了，但是还得转移下她的注意力，因为她的撒娇应该多半是想让我去看她或者陪陪她，所以千万不要着急踢球而想挂电话，而要多跟她聊一会儿，顺便跟她说”我打算买某天的电影票，你这两天一定要在家好好休养，可别到时候再哪里不舒服哟，我们还要一起去逛街看电影呢！“这样一来，今天的球虽然可能得晚点去踢，但是不会泡汤。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7671,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492093819000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Echo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0b57ibH6T3V3jNd7HDHXPdJagbpJpZ0oYN9srsbXbOyiaZS0Cqia5uToJn7saia4Gpsd3G2eB7siaedh/0","content":"是真的不太舒服，还是想我了？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7641,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492067997000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Frank Wan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69mgoQxwst1pOnyjgzqvAdFLicrRtQ1EftWszvwz9E0AjlKicpvTt2ticDuiaGDvlMcUexZCPNSjNib2Cw/0","content":"哪里不舒服呀？<div>需要我带你去医院吗？</div><div>是不是想我了呀宝宝？<br><div>我踢完球去陪你好不好？</div><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7635,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492057308000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"柚子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZTxBjA1yfvJcK6vUiaZbqRQAicAjPVuGLUfeibCkKPCfsQSnY8PdnPfAO0ochpiccXQQWNkg8U0DK8SVvwQlZ8QQUm/0","content":"提问：为什么不舒服呢？出发点是不是因为不想让老公去踢球？<div>为什么不想让他去踢球呢？真正需求是想让他多陪。</div><div>可以通过在踢球外多安排时间来陪来实现</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7551,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491922066000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Huiling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSibLgdZoEbwz0j0N3JqxibHIXiaPrzMn0EqK1SiaZOmddjg9AV56OBReweicArAW1qtlxy36IJF04ibrj2/0","content":"需要我来陪你么？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7536,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491913914000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6Kq7NwJg01KPhAdTxrtB27YOCDyNYflqVmOChkOmM1s8UJogTLQGWiaichDH2J1MHWWX9TCzzgwDAYgS/0","content":"<p><b>澄清需求</b></p><p>小明的需求：兼顾爱情、友情和自己的利益</p><p>女友的需求：声称是身体不太舒服，真是可能是需要男友陪伴、有事商量，或两者兼有</p><p>提问：为什么身体不太舒服？要不要我陪你啊？</p><p>思考：</p><p>女友可能是现在需要我陪伴，她伤心或者不高兴了。但知道我要踢球又不好意思直说。</p><p>回忆最近女友的状态，现在这样反常吗？</p><p><b>如何实现</b></p><p>女友需要</p><p>看病：先休息，喝点热水；紧急的话小明立即找女友</p><p>找人陪：可不可以找室友或闺蜜</p><p>有事商量：在电话里说说怎么回事</p><p><b>我如何做</b></p><p>提问：是不是着凉了？要不要去医院啊？你先休息着，我马上找你</p><p>行动：如果球赛不是很紧急就找别人踢比赛，陪女友，还可以带个小礼物哄她开心</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7504,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491877988000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"<p>身体不舒服啊？有没有去看医生呀？那我现在过去陪陪妳</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7501,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491877144000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"<p><img alt=\"小明.jpg\" style=\"max-width:90%\" src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170410225817-80a3pihqz.jpg\"><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7485,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491836306000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p>小明：啊，你身体那里不舒服了？是昨天出去受凉了？要不要我过来陪你？</p><p>女朋友：我没什么事，就是有点懒懒的没精神。你先去踢球吧。</p><p>小明：那你先在家休息一会。因为都和朋友约好了，一下不好推掉。我踢完球过来看给。给你买最爱的甜点，好么？</p><p>女朋友：好的。</p><p><br></p><p>还是要先了解情况，身体不舒服到底到什么程度了。如果很严重的话，还是要先去看女朋友。如果还不是那么紧急，就先安抚情绪，踢好球后再去。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7453,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491793835000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPsccICKmhqibTHZ3c6PRPlXKQOMsQGCZVTGNkMa0625BIPiaGC4